title: Women Need Each Other
itunes:author: Guest: Dr. Meg Meeker
itunes:summary: Competition between women and moms isn’t always a bad thing, but John and Danny discuss the fact that women need each other, so they can't let competition hurt their relationships. Receive the book The 10 Habits of Happy Mothers with your gift of any amount!
